snippet.title: Vestige of the Past - Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
In-game video footage from Vestige of the Past showing basic game mechanics in an early pre-alpha stage.

Developed in Brno, Vestige of the Past is a unique blend of open world survival, exploration and simulation games.

Steam Greenlight - www.steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=783007718

Early Access of Vestige of the Past will be released in Q1 2017 on PC.
